== Description ==
{{Description|Night Shrimp are small, versatile crustaceans that can be found in an abundance in Vertigo's calm water. night Shrimp are predominantly diurnal, making day fishing the most effective time.|Bestiary Entry}}

== Obtainment ==
{{Description|Caught with crab cages in Vertigo.|Bestiary Hint}}

== Catch Quips ==
When catching a Night Shrimp, the player has a chance to make one of the following exclamations:
* A Night Shrimp!
* Woah! A Night Shrimp
* Awesome!
* A Night Shrimp!
* Ou! A Night Shrimpy!

